# {{ name }}

Private Kansei control plane instance.

This workspace keeps local project registry, provider registry, dashboards,
runbooks, prompts, and private knowledge. Project source trees remain in their
own repositories.

Activate the local environment created by `kansei init`:

```powershell
.venv\Scripts\activate
kansei doctor
```

If HarnessOps was available during `kansei init`, this instance also has a
`harness-feedback/` overlay managed by `hops`. Update it through
`kansei update-harness` or `hops update-harness`; do not manually restructure
`.harnessops/` or `harness-feedback/`.
